Package: tls-snoop
Version: VERSION_PLACEHOLDER
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: zarak <zarak.tls@zarak.fr>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-click, python3-scapy, python3-pyroute2, python3-prometheus-client, bpfcc-tools
Homepage: https://github.com/fayak/tls-snoop
Description: eBPF-based TLS handshake capture daemon
 TLS Snoop uses eBPF/TC hooks to capture TLS Client Hello and Server Hello
 messages from network traffic. It outputs transaction metadata as NDJSON
 and exposes Prometheus metrics for monitoring TLS version and cipher
 suite usage across your network.
